DAoC Style Graves and Bindstones<br>
----------------------------------<br>
<br>
This script implements Dark Age of Camelot style graves and bindstones.<br>
<br>
When you die a grave will be erected where you died.<br>
You can return to your grave to regain a DM definable percentage of the XP lost. If you die again before praying at the grave, the old grave will be destroyed.<br>
<br>
Also it implements bindstones which allow you to set them as your respawn point and to get information on your last grave.<br>
<br>
Note: I set the graves to be easily destroyed to prevent them from blocking other players.<br>
<br>
Contains 2 placeables (grave and bindstone) as well as a custom Module OnClientEnter and OnPlayerRespawn scripts.<br>
